title: MS2extractDB: small molecules MS/MS (ESI-QTOF) database repository
text: goal MS2extractDB stored MS/MS data set authentic small molecules standards, including, phenolic acids, flavonoids, dihydrochalcones, carbohydrates. Standards collected using Agilent QTOF 6545 6546, negative positive polarities, 20 60 eV (CE). Standards collected using 6546 QTOF also contains MS/MS 60 80 eV (CE). raw MS/MS files used jointly MS2extract package create -house MS/MS libaries.

title: MS2extractDB: small molecules MS/MS (ESI-QTOF) database repository
text: package intended archive raw mzml files authentic standards, well structurated data frames used MS2extract automate process creating -house MS/MS library database contains majorly phenolics compounds, aimed decipher rosacea metabolome. However, phenolics expressed wide range organisms, database can used multiples scenarios. grouped total database two batches. two batches based instrument used acquire data. first batch, used Agilent QTOF 6545, second batch, used Agilent QTOF 6546. batches, collected targeted MS/MS, using chromatographic method reported Bilbrey al. (2022). batches, collected data negative positive polarities, used 20 40 eV (CE) using CID.
